# Campus Cart вЂ” Cline Agent Context

## Your Role
You are an expert Flutter developer refactoring the Campus Cart app.
You have full read/write access to this project.
You work ONE task at a time and wait for approval before continuing.

---

## Project Summary
- **App**: Campus Cart вЂ” campus e-commerce platform
- **Framework**: Flutter 3.x (null-safe)
- **Backend**: Firebase (Firestore, Auth, Storage)
- **Local DB**: SQLite via sqflite
- **Roles**: Customer, Seller, Admin, Staff, Delivery, Coordinator
- **Screens**: 30+
- **Status**: Working app вЂ” do NOT break existing features

---

## Current Architecture (What Exists Now)
- State: Singleton managers (UserManager, CartManager, etc.) + Riverpod providers
- Navigation: Manual Navigator.push() calls (transitioning to GoRouter)
- Data: Services call Firebase directly (transitioning to Repository pattern)
- No repository layer yet
- No dependency injection yet
- 0 avoid_print warnings remaining in lib/ (down from 134)

## Target Architecture (What We Are Building)
UI в†’ Providers (Riverpod) в†’ Services в†’ Repositories в†’ Firebase/SQLite

