## Absolute Rules вЂ” Never Break These
1. Never change UI design, colors, or layouts
2. Never remove existing screens or features
3. Never rename Firebase collection names or document fields
4. Never change existing model class structures
5. Never do more than one task at a time
6. Always run flutter analyze after each task
7. Always fix new errors before moving to next task
8. If unsure about existing logic в†’ ASK before changing
9. If a task creates more than 5 new errors в†’ STOP and report
10. All code must be null-safe (Flutter 3.x)

